Units- 

px - fixed 
% - depending on parent 
vw - viewport width (depending on screen width)
vh - viewport height (depending on screen height)
vmax- viewport maximum
vmin- viewport minimum
em - parent ko value de or sare childs ko em me value dedo  or parent ki value change karenge to sare childs ki value bhi change hogi
rem - 16px( according to the root)
ch -  ye kisi bhi word me kitane charecter hai unper focuse karta hai , es 'ch' se ham ye diside kar sakte hai ki one line me kitane charecter aayenge
lh -  ye two santance ya word ke bich gap abanata hai . 

display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
justify-content:space-evenly;